snippet.title: GUILTY GEAR: The Missing Link (PC) - Intro / Opening
snippet.description:
Intro / Opening of the the PC version of the first Guilty Gear: The Missing Link.

🎮 Learn the moves of the characters in the GG ML playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLOO2o6Kew2GNEJB-9_Kd-ZEk-oQH2p3S7

Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_YL558gxlL_SsFdw5MOJ1QjgLiM8sg79

Release data:
Guilty Gear (2019) / (1998 - Original Release for Playstation)
Genre: Fighting
Platform: PC  (Steam)
Developer: Arc System Works

Recorded at 60 fps with Live Gamer Portable 2 - GC510, 60fps 1080p.
